{"tid":462103,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺d人結婚去酒樓擺酒好撚cheap","createTime":"2017-11-08T09:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T09:11:23.000Z","uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec8c9c0fa7597994ddc631222420bac6951fa05","tid":462103,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"去酒樓擺酒 基本上同同人講自己係死窮西無分別<br />\n正常黎計一生人得一既野<br />\n連幾皮野都慳<br />\n就可以知一個人成功極有限<br />\n去酒店擺酒其實真係好基本<br />\n多數去酒樓多d都係公屋窮撚黎<br />\n之前有人派貼，寫住乜乜酒樓<br />\n我已經忍唔住當面笑左<br />\n我諗條女d姊妹背後都會暗地講佢壞話話乜佢老公窮撚黎<br />\n講真 走酒樓搞，不如去m記算啦"},{"pid":"9c12ff22db1a65cd54af8dbf36d15462e6aee429","tid":462103,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d6641b9084fe43d3d53f08430d111f4b099eb65","tid":462103,"uid":153245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"咁你呢 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">女你都無啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea752028b4724e7baea8f68b1bf29a539b5967b7","tid":462103,"uid":132981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主去大酒店擺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑撚左~"},{"pid":"633056d8dd178f991e09cebf5a2615acdc405dbe","tid":462103,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}